    pc "O meu nome é..."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:52
translate portuguese izzy2_28bea8fd:

    # "Just then the chirp of a police siren and a flashing light in the distance catches everyone's attention."
    "Nesse momento, o som de uma sirene da polícia e uma luz intermitente ao longe chamam a atenção de todos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:55
translate portuguese izzy2_40384605:

    # mal "Cops!"
    mal "Polícia!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:56
translate portuguese izzy2_3a4267e8:

    # moose "Oh shit, I gotta get out of here!"
    moose "Oh merda, tenho de sair daqui!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:57
translate portuguese izzy2_db9ea3d3:

    # gl "Damn, gotta split."
    gl "Raios, tenho de me despachar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:60
translate portuguese izzy2_84f98777:

    # gl "You come back and hang out with us sometime."
    gl "Volta e passa tempo connosco um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:61
translate portuguese izzy2_37f4bf94:

    # gl "We know how to have a good time."
    gl "Sabemos como nos divertir."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:62
translate portuguese izzy2_d2b269a7:

    # gl "See you later, Twig."
    gl "Até logo, Twig."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:65
translate portuguese izzy2_dbce667a:

    # "With that, she runs off in the same direction as the others."
    "Dito isto, ela sai a correr na mesma direção que os outros."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:66
translate portuguese izzy2_4f647b81:

    # "I turn and walk back to my car."
    "Viro-me e volto para o meu carro."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:67
translate portuguese izzy2_56b73e22:

    # "The police sirens and lights fade away. I'm not even sure they were aware of Izzy and her gang."
    "As sirenes e as luzes da polícia vão-se afastando. Nem tenho a certeza se eles se aperceberam da Izzy e do seu grupo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:68
translate portuguese izzy2_b8cda32c:

    # "I wonder why they are so jumpy?"
    "Por que é que eles estão tão nervosos?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy2.rpy:69
translate portuguese izzy2_b0b60482:

    # "I'll have to come back and hang out with them some other time. For now I get in my car and drive away."
    "Vou ter de voltar para sair com eles noutra altura. Por agora, entro no meu carro e vou-me embora."

